 VTuber“Shintowai”和“Amarou Konomi”进入“2023年日本YouTube年度排名” https://www.moguravr.com/youtube-2023-ranking/MoguLive編集部 Wed, 13 Dec 2023 02:30:38 +0000 VTuber新兎わい甘狼このみ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=241909 <p> 12月13日星期三，YouTube官方公布了《2023年日本YouTube年度排名》。据透露，VTuber Shintowai 和 Kanomi Konomi 均上榜。根据官方声明，Shintowai-san [...]</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/youtube-2023-ranking/">VTuber“Shintowai”和“Amarou Konomi”首先出现</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> 12月13日星期三，YouTube官方公布了《 <a href="https://youtube-jp.googleblog.com/2023/12/2023YTJPEOYranking.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2023年日本YouTube年度排名</a>》。据透露，VTuber <a href="https://twitter.com/nitowai_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shintowai</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/AmakamiKonomi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kanomi Konomi</a>均上榜。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rtvkzdy0gofc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rtvkzdy0gofc-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rtvkzdy0gofc-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rtvkzdy0gofc-300x150.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rtvkzdy0gofc-768x384.webp 768w" width="800" height="400" /></a></p><p>据官网显示，Shintowai 在“<strong>订阅人数增加的顶级创作者</strong>”类别（2023 年内订阅人数大幅增加的频道排名，不包括艺术家和品牌）排名第 10。 Konomi Amaro 在“<strong>快速增长创作者</strong>”类别（2023 年内订户数量较去年大幅增加的频道排名，不包括艺术家和品牌）排名第 9。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.o6ojocsu324l-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8997bd7cea5c0942f33f4272bd05caf8-kix.rgxsrnsqlwa3-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p> Shintowai是一名VTuber，因挑战益智游戏“Q”的短视频而受到关注，她公开介绍过去的尴尬情节，并发布自己在现实生活中跳舞的视频，也以其风格而闻名。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="NaniColle 哈哈 你是怎么做到的？ ？ ？ ？ #shorts #Shintowai #nitowai [Q Remastered]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/837mSgWP9Es" width="656" height="1167" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p> Konomi Amaro 是一位 VTuber，同时也是一名插画师，她在她的短视频中以简短易懂的方式解释了如何绘制插图以及如何对 Live2D 进行建模。今年，一段解释如何画漫画《忍之子》中人物眼睛的视频获得了高度好评。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[Oshi no Ko]我真的很想成为“星野爱”，所以我成为了其中之一[#Amarou Konomi]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Pf7ocg5JyR4" width="656" height="1167" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://youtube-jp.googleblog.com/2023/12/2023YTJPEOYranking.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处查看“2023年日本YouTube年度排名”结果详情</a></p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/youtube-2023-ranking/">VTuber“Shintowai”和“Amarou Konomi”首先出现</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
